full_text: Form 1 - 181a (Rev. 4-1-77)Y UNITED STATES DEPARTMENT OF JUSTICE IMMIGRATION AND NATURALIZATION SERVICE REFER TO THIS FILE NO. A 21 344 739 CIN Date: NGUYEN, Than Thi 2999 Mendoza Dr. #A Costa Mesa, California 92626 Your application for status as a permanent resident has been received. When proc- essing has been completed, you will be invited to appear for medical examination and interview. To avoid delay in the processing of your application, please do not telephone or write while your case is pending. However, if there is a change in your address, employ- ment or marital status, please notify this office promptly by mail referring to the above file number. Sincerely yours, District Director (Page 3)
